OL,3,CGrant Shapps urges Chancellor to raise
OL,4,Cdefence spending to 2.5% of GDP
OL,6,FDefence Secretary Grant Shapps has
OL,7,Furged the Chancellor to increase
OL,8,Fmilitary spending to 2.5% of GDP at
OL,9,Fnext week's Budget.
OL,11,FIn a letter first reported by the
OL,12,FDaily Telegraph and since confirmed by
OL,13,Fthe Ministry of Defence (MoD), Mr
OL,14,FShapps wrote to Jeremy Hunt saying: "I
OL,15,Fbelieve we must take bold action in
OL,16,Fyour Budget in March to commit to
OL,17,Fdefence spending increasing to 2.5% in
OL,18,F2024.
