OL,3,CGrant Shapps urges Chancellor to raise
OL,4,Cdefence spending to 2.5% of GDP
OL,6,F"This will resonate with our allies
OL,7,Fand adversaries. It would re-establish
OL,8,Four leadership in Europe."
OL,10,FThe MoD said the extract of the
OL,11,Fletter, reportedly sent on January 24,
OL,12,Fwas accurate but that it was not
OL,13,Fsharing the correspondence between the
OL,14,Fsenior Government ministers more
OL,15,Fwidely.
OL,17,FThe Treasury, which said it would not
OL,18,Fcomment on speculation ahead of
OL,19,FWednesday's fiscal event, pointed to
OL,20,Fextra defence investment in last
OL,21,Fyear's Budget in its response.
