OL,3,CGrant Shapps urges Chancellor to raise
OL,4,Cdefence spending to 2.5% of GDP
OL,6,FPrime Minister Rishi Sunak has said he
OL,7,Fwants to raise defence spending to
OL,8,F2.5% of GDP, a measure of the size of
OL,9,Fthe economy, when economic
OL,10,Fcircumstances allow.
OL,12,FThe Telegraph's report suggested the
OL,13,Fincrease to 2.5% would cost about an
OL,14,Fextra #9 billion.
