OL,3,CGrant Shapps urges Chancellor to raise
OL,4,Cdefence spending to 2.5% of GDP
OL,6,FTreasury sources this week said Mr
OL,7,FHunt is considering a further squeeze
OL,8,Fon public spending as a way to deliver
OL,9,Fthe tax cuts being demanded by some
OL,10,FTory MPs.
OL,12,FMr Shapps, after visiting British and
OL,13,FUkrainian soldiers in North Yorkshire
OL,14,Fon Thursday, spoke to reporters about
OL,15,FBritain's defence spending and
OL,16,Fappeared to confirm he had lobbied the
OL,17,FTreasury for additional funds.
