OL,3,CGrant Shapps urges Chancellor to raise
OL,4,Cdefence spending to 2.5% of GDP
OL,6,F"As you would expect, I'm a secretary
OL,7,Fof state who lobbies hard for the area
OL,8,Fthat I represent and I happen to think
OL,9,Fthat, in this case, the defence of our
OL,10,Fnation is our number one priority.
OL,12,F"The first thing a government has to
OL,13,Fdo is make sure it secures its borders
OL,14,Fand is able to defend itself.
OL,16,F"I am pretty full throttle in my
OL,17,Finsistence that that is what we do."
